<plot>In 1944 the writer Julio Cortázar lived in Chivilcoy, there he met the photographer Ignacio Tankel. Together they wrote the screenplay "La sombra del pasado". Sixty years later, people from Chivilcoy asked what happened with that film and with Cortázar and Tankel's friendship.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?087464</url></doc>
